{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee-dor-saint","title":"D'OR SAINT - Ltd. Ed.","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Cropped Ringer Design. Embroidered Front Detail. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Limited Edition (100 Pieces). Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis exclusive 240 GSM cropped ringer T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted to deliver a refined balance of vintage inspiration and modern luxury. Designed with signature contrast ringer trims on the neckline and sleeves, it features a clean cropped silhouette with a relaxed waist that offers effortless structure and comfort. The front is elevated with a finely embroidered detail that adds a subtle yet premium statement without overpowering the minimal aesthetic. Made from high-grade combed and bio-washed cotton, the fabric feels exceptionally soft, breathable, and durable for everyday wear. Strictly limited to only 100 pieces, this piece is designed for those who appreciate exclusivity, precision, and timeless streetwear luxury.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"99\" data-start=\"60\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and preserve the embroidery. Avoid harsh detergents or bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the structure. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and embroidery finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium cotton fabric delivering a structured yet comfortable feel. Cropped ringer silhouette with contrast neckline and sleeve trims for a timeless aesthetic. Finely embroidered front detail adding a subtle luxury statement. Regular-fit cropped design with a relaxed waist for balanced structure and movement. Gender-neutral silhouette suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton ensures all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish for enhanced softness and long-term durability. Exclusively limited to only 100 pieces.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47631552643226,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47631552675994,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47631552708762,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47631552741530,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/Copy_of_DSC00085_copy.jpg_11zon_1.webp?v=1773674828","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/regular-cropped-tee-dor-saint","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}